Package: balancing
Title: Bregman Balancing Weights
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("David", "Hirshberg", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "david.a.hirshberg@gmail.com")
Description: Kernel balancing weights via Bregman method-of-moments with
    pluggable dispersions, kernels, and estimands. Supports survival and
    single-outcome settings with adaptive regularization (Lepski) and
    cross-fitting.
